_sText:
This is my third CS : Source map, and it includes
 good graphics for an fy map and strategic spots 
for shootouts. The map contains a detailed cybercafe 
with breakable computers and file cabinets to save 
your head! The middle of the map contains the 
traditional "quad area" but in high graphical detail. 
I spent time on this map to ensure it was done right! 
The map supports 32 players yet 16 recommended for 
performance. Most of all have fun!
